{"type":"message","id":"04adab39","parentId":"0227606e","timestamp":"2026-06-01T07:25:15.701Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the current configuration. Let me analyze the token usage optimization opportunities:\n\nCurrent model: MiniMax M2.7 with 204k context window\nCurrent usage: 47k in / 47k out (23% usage)\n\nFor MiniMax 3.0, the user mentioned usage is low (\"用量可怜\"), so we should consider optimization strategies.\n\nLet me think about token optimization approaches:\n\n1. **Compaction settings** - The current compaction mode is \"safeguard\" which is conservative. We could be more aggressive.\n\n2. **Context management** - Using lossless-claw but could optimize summary frequency\n\n3. **System prompt trimming** - The loaded project context files (AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md, USER.md, TOOLS.md, MEMORY.md, HEARTBEAT.md) are quite large and loaded every time.\n\n4. **Thinking mode** - Currently \"adaptive\" - could consider reducing thinking for simpler tasks\n\n5. **Model fallbacks** - Already have fallbacks to free models\n\nLet me look at what specific optimizations we can make:\n\n1. **Reduce system prompt size** - The workspace files loaded are substantial. We could trim these or make them more concise.\n\n2. **Adjust compaction** - More aggressive compaction to reduce context history size\n\n3. **Thinking settings** - \"adaptive\" might be generating extra thinking tokens for simple queries\n\n4. **Model configuration** - Add MiniMax 3.0 if available, and configure appropriate maxTokens\n\nLet me search for MiniMax 3.0 information to understand what's available.\n","thinkingSignature":"27c7aeaf0b97db60630e8ec1c88bc103e6a1ba858e3987bd75adf4aea1a0b7a9"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n让我了解一下 MiniMax 3.0 的情况，然后给出优化建议。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ny903ij1wre0_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"MiniMax 3.0 发布 context window 价格 2026","search_lang":"zh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provi