{"type":"message","id":"9c70aa6a","parentId":"b27a4904","timestamp":"2026-06-01T07:25:45.210Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Web search isn't configured. Let me try to search for info about MiniMax 3.0 through other means. Let me think about what I know and can do.\n\nThe user is asking about optimizing token usage since MiniMax 3.0 is out and apparently has very limited usage/quota (\"用量可怜\"). Let me think about token optimization strategies for the current setup.\n\nBased on the config I can see:\n- MiniMax-M2.7 has context window of 204000 tokens\n- Currently using minimax as primary with fallbacks to openrouter models\n\nToken optimization strategies:\n1. **Switch to a cheaper model for simple tasks** - The fallbacks include deepseek-v4-flash:free which is free\n2. **Compact conversation history** - Already using lossless-claw with safeguard mode\n3. **Adjust compaction settings** - Could make compaction more aggressive\n4. **Use lighter model for subagents** - tts agent could use a cheaper model\n5. **System prompt optimization** - Reduce system prompt size\n6. **Thinking mode** - Adaptive thinking uses more tokens; could set to minimal\n7. **Limit context inclusion** - Use lightContext for spawned subagents\n\nLet me suggest practical optimizations given the current setup.\n","thinkingSignature":"0facc2644a42b31773f33920b2f9a037b6a7bc167a7f37bcc73dd662e4ad500d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n没搜到3.0的具体信息，不过根据用量\"可怜\"这个描述，我猜是配额限量或者价格较贵。来看看能怎么省 token：\n\n**当前配置分析：**\n- Primary：`MiniMax-M2.7`（context 204k，输入成本应该最高）\n- Fallbacks：`deepseek-v4-flash:free` / `gpt-4o-mini` 等\n\n**优化方向：**\n\n1. **简单任务走免费模型** — deepseek-v4-flash:free 完全可以处理普通对话，把 `minimax` 降为 fallback，主要走免费模型，省下的额度留给真正需要的时候。\n\n2. **Subagent 用轻量模型** — `tts` 等子 Agent 现在也用 M2.7，可以切到 `gpt-4o-mini` 或 `deepseek-v4-flash`，便宜很多。\n\n3. **compaction 调激进一点** — 当前是 `safeguard` 模式（只保安全），可以改成更激进的压缩，减少历史记忆的 token 消耗。\n\n4. **thinking 默认关掉** — `thinkingDefault: \"adaptive\"` 会让模型主动展开推理，关掉或设 `off` 能省不少。\n\n5. **LightContext for subagents** — 派生子任务时用 `lightContext: true`，不带完整历史，只给必要信息。\n\n你想先试哪个方向？还是我来帮你配一版省 token 的配置？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":135,"output":559,"cacheRead":50816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51510,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780298736318,"responseId":"066c66f051987dc1939eb31f7a4d942c"}}
